citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process between 1:25 pm and
2:00 pm on 01-AUG-2023. There was no answer when I knocked on the door of the residence. There was no answer to
phone calls at 1:31 pm and 1:58 pm. Messages were left each time. I left the facility at 2:00 pm.
End Section
